You may also need testing to make sure you have effective immunity. If not, you may need to try another vaccine. Or another dose. If you understand the history of vaccines, creating a Covid-19 vaccine will be a lifetime achievement. This is not just about winning the Olympic gold medal. That is if a specific decisive vaccine is created, causing the disease to be rendered inert.



